{"summary":"<blockquote><p>使用PHP7</p>\n</blockquote>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"PHP-FPM：7-1-x\"><a href=\"#PHP-FPM：7-1-x\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"PHP-FPM：7.1.x\"></a>PHP-FPM：<code>7.1.x</code></h2><p>安装并启用<code>remi</code>源包，这个源包含有最新的稳定版<code>PHP</code>：<br><figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> yum install https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/remi/enterprise/remi-release-6.rpm</span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#</span><span class=\"bash\"> vim /etc/yum.repos.d/remi-php71.repo</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>修改一下代码，启用此源（否则会找不到PHP7）：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>[remi-php71]<br>……<br>enabled=0</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>To：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>enabled=1</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>现在，重新检查版本并安装：<br><figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><div class=\"line\">1</div><div class=\"line\">2</div><div class=\"line\">3</div><div class=\"line\">4</div><div class=\"line\">5</div></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><div class=\"line\"># <span class=\"selector-tag\">yum</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">list</span> <span class=\"selector-tag\">php-fpm</span></div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">php-fpm</span><span class=\"selector-class\">.x86_64</span>   7<span class=\"selector-class\">.1</span><span class=\"selector-class\">.0-1</span><span class=\"selector-class\">.el6</span><span class=\"selector-class\">.remi</span>   @<span class=\"keyword\">remi</span>-<span class=\"keyword\">php71</span></div><div class=\"line\"></div><div class=\"line\"># yum install php-fpm</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<h2 id=\"参考资料\"><a href=\"#参考资料\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考资料\"></a>参考资料</h2><ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.cnblogs.com/jtnote/p/6118741.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external\">yum安装php，php-fpm</a></li>\n</ul>\n"}